{"lemma":"غَشْيَة","slug":"غَشْيَة","root":"غ.ش.#","root_slug":"غ-ش-_","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ش-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"غَشْي","root":"غشو","pos":"V","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31900","n31907","n31908"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%B4%D9%92%D9%8A%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cover up, to cover over"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cover up, to cover over; to enfold, to envelop, to wrap up"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣaʃ.ʃaː/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31900","headword_ar":"غَشِيَهُ","root":"g$w and g$Y","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yago$aY","text_ar":"يَغْشَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$aAwapN","text_ar":"غَشَاوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It covered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tg$~Ahu","text_ar":"تغشّاهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (MA.) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$aAniY All~ayolu","text_ar":"غَشَانِى اللَّيْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iyaniY","text_ar":"غَشِيَنِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The night covered me,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed me:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the meaning may be that which next follows]. (JK.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iyahu","text_ar":"غَشِيَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (TA,) is said of an event ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amorN","text_ar":"اَمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"), [and of heat, (S and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dgm","text_ar":"دغم"},{"kind":"text","text":",) and of cold, (K in that art.,) and of an affection of the mind or body, and of various things, sometimes in like manner of a man, and of a company of men,] in a similar sense; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tg$~Ahu","text_ar":"تغشّاهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) both signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It came upon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"invaded, so as to surprise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to over-whelm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"properly meaning]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as a thing that covered, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) Hence, in the Kur [liii. 16],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*o yago$aY A@lsi~dorapa maA yago$aY","text_ar":"اـِذْ يَغْشَى ا@لسِّدْرَةَ مَا يَغْشَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When there was coming upon the lote-tree so as to cover it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overspread it, what was so coming"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And in the same [xx. 81],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faga$iyahumo mina A@loyam~i maA ga$iyahumo","text_ar":"فَغَشِيَهُمْ مِنَ ا@لْيَمِّ مَا غَشِيَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And there came upon them so as to overwhelm them, of the sea, what so came upon them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And in the same [viii. 11],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*o yago$aAkumu","text_ar":"اـِذْ يَغْشَاكُمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[followed by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@Aln~uEaAsu","text_ar":"ا@النُّعَاسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(drowsiness)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was coming upon you,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overcoming you"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; accord. to one reading; other readings being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yugo$iykumu","text_ar":"يُغْشِيكُمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuga$~iykumu","text_ar":"يُغَشِّيكُمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[followed by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ln~uEaAsa","text_ar":"ا@لنُّعَاسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaA$iyapN","text_ar":"غَاشِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places. ―         -b3-  [A somewhat similar signification of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iyahu","text_ar":"غَشِيَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"will be found below.] ―         -b4-  One says of the night,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yago$aY biZulomatihi kul~a maA bayona","text_ar":"يَغْشَى بِظُلْمَتِهِ كُلَّ مَا بَيْنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~amaA='i waAlA^aroDi","text_ar":"السَّمَا=ءِ وَالاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It covers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conceals, with its darkness, everything that is between the heaven and the earth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Jel in xcii. 1.) And [hence it is said that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iYa All~ayolu","text_ar":"غَشِىَ اللَّيْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The night was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, dark;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ag$Y","text_ar":"اغشى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, TA.) ―         -b5-  [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iyahu","text_ar":"غَشِيَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iYa baSarahu","text_ar":"غَشِىَ بَصَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"g$~Ahu","text_ar":"غشّاهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. light ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dawo'N","text_ar":"ضَوْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came upon him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon his eye, with an overpowering effect, so as to obscure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dazzle, his sight."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iyahu","text_ar":"غَشِيَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='ahu","text_ar":"جَا=ءَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataAhu","text_ar":"اَتَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, K) [which have two meanings, i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"both, perhaps, here meant, for both are well-known meanings of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iyahu","text_ar":"غَشِيَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and, thus used, the aor. is as above, (TA,) and the inf. n. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$ayaAnN","text_ar":"غَشَيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gi$oyaAnN","text_ar":"غِشْيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in one of my copies of the S,) or the subst. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gi$oyaAnN","text_ar":"غِشْيَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) with kesr, (Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_itoyaAnN","text_ar":"اـِتْيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iYa fulaAnFA","text_ar":"غَشِىَ فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came to such a one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataAhu","text_ar":"اَتَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$aAhu","text_ar":"غَشَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yago$uwhu","text_ar":"يَغْشُوهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b7-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iyahaA","text_ar":"غَشِيَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, MA, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$ayaAnN","text_ar":"غَشَيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gi$oyaAnN","text_ar":"غِشْيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (accord. to different copies of the S,) or the latter and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$oYN","text_ar":"غَشْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MA,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gi$oyaAnN","text_ar":"غِشْيَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the subst. in this case also, (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_itoyaAnN","text_ar":"اـِتْيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", metonymically used in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jimaAEN","text_ar":"جِمَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, Msb,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He compressed her;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, MA, Msb, K;) namely, a woman; (MA, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tg$~AhA","text_ar":"تغشّاها","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (MA, Msb, TA.) ―         -b8-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iYa","text_ar":"غَشِىَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayohi maHojarFA","text_ar":"اـِلَيْهِ مَحْجَرًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataY A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اَتَى اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a forbidden action."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hjr","text_ar":"حجر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [Hence,] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gi$oyaAnu","text_ar":"غِشْيَانُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaHaArimi","text_ar":"المَحَارِمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The doing of forbidden things"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh and Msb and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rhq","text_ar":"رهق"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iYa Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"غَشِىَ الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He occupied himself with the thing, engaged in it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"personally managed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conducted it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laAbasahu","text_ar":"لَابَسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baA$arahu","text_ar":"بَاشَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (JM.) [And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tg$~Y","text_ar":"تغشّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has a similar meaning; for it is said that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aga$~iY","text_ar":"التَّغَشِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alga$oYu","text_ar":"الغَشْىُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"primarily signify"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_itoyaAnu","text_ar":"الاـِتْيَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmulaAbasapu","text_ar":"المُلَابَسَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and they took an extended range in using the former, so that one said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlEadoli","text_ar":"بِالعَدْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taga$~aAhumo","text_ar":"تَغَشَّاهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlojawori","text_ar":"بِالْجَوْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ruled them with equity"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with injustice"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Ham p. 27.) [And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yago$aY","text_ar":"يَغْشَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHuruwba","text_ar":"الحُرُوبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see Ham p. 27), meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He plunges into wars, or battles:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugaAmisN","text_ar":"مُغَامِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and its verb.] ―         -b9-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iyahu biAls~awoTi","text_ar":"غَشِيَهُ بِالسَّوْطِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, in which it is said to be like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raDiyahu","text_ar":"رَضِيَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and so accord. to some copies of the S, the phrase in these being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$iyatu","text_ar":"غَشِيَتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~ajula biAls~awoTi","text_ar":"الرَّجُلَ بِالسَّوْطِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$~aAhu","text_ar":"غَشَّاهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (accord. to other copies of the S, the verb in these being written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$~ayotu","text_ar":"غَشَّيْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and thus accord. to an explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qan~aEa","text_ar":"قَنَّعَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^osahu biAls~awoTi","text_ar":"رَاْسَهُ بِالسَّوْطِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qnE","text_ar":"قنع"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He struck him"},{"kind":"text","text":"(i. e. a man, S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the whip; he flogged him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gu$iYa Ealayohi","text_ar":"غُشِىَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, MA, Mgh, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$oYN","text_ar":"غَشْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, * K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gu$oYN","text_ar":"غُشْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MA,) or both, (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$ayaAnN","text_ar":"غَشَيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA, and so in some copies of the S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gi$oyaAnN","text_ar":"غِشْيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in other copies of the S,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$oyapN","text_ar":"غَشْيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh,) or this last is an inf. n. of un., (Msb,) or it is the subst., (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He swooned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became senseless:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, PS:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ugomiYa Ealayohi","text_ar":"اُغْمِىَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: (K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alga$oYu","text_ar":"الغَشْىُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Algu$oYu","text_ar":"الغُشْىُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"page_break","n":2262},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a state of inertness"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEaT~ul","text_ar":"تَعَطُّل"},{"kind":"text","text":", Mgh, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the motive and sensitive faculties,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the motive faculties and of the sensitive will,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on account of the weakness of the heart,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the soul's becoming drawn together thereto by a cause that suppresses it"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuxofiyhi","text_ar":"يُخْفِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"within so that it finds not a place of passage, and of the causes thereof is a strangling"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stifling"},{"kind":"text","text":"], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurtful, cold repletion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehement hunger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehement pain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cold,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excessive hunger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an evil affection in some associate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"participating, organ, such as the heart and the stomach:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) some say that it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_igomaA='u","text_ar":"الاـِغْمَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for which see its proper art.]; (Mgh, Msb;) thus say the scholastic theologians: (Mgh:) others (the physicians and the lawyers, Mgh) make a difference between these two terms. (Mgh, Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","Mgh","Msb","MA","PS"]},{"entry_id":"n31907","headword_ar":"غَشْيَةٌ","root":"g$w and g$Y","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of the verb in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gu$iYa","text_ar":"غُشِىَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh,) or the subst, thereof, (K,) or the inf. n. un. thereof [signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A swoon"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) See 1, last sentence. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$oyapu Almawoti","text_ar":"غَشْيَةُ المَوْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The clouding"},{"kind":"text","text":"(lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covering"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the understanding that befalls a man on the occasion of death."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$oyapu Hum~aY","text_ar":"غَشْيَةُ حُمَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A touch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slight attack, of fever."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K"]},{"entry_id":"n31908","headword_ar":"غُشْيَةٌ","root":"g$w and g$Y","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gi$aAwapN","text_ar":"غِشَاوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}